Tavily-powered image search script. Fetches 1 image per scene (30 total). Each scene IS a single 3-second cut — no intra-scene cycling needed. Follows the established `fetch-images-tavily.ts` pattern.

#### [NEW] [generate-voiceover-mythos.ts](file:///c:/Users/ADMIN/Desktop/AInewsvideo/scripts/generate-voiceover-mythos.ts)
