2. `npx tsx scripts/fetch-images-mythos.ts` — Confirm 30 image downloads from Tavily
3. `npm run dev` — Open Remotion Studio, preview `mythos-short` composition
4. Verify total duration ≈ 2700 frames (90s × 30fps)
5. Confirm word-synced captions align with audio playback
6. Confirm 30 distinct visual cuts (one per scene boundary)

### Manual Verification
- Preview full video in Remotion Studio at 1× speed
- Verify all 30 scene transitions are smooth (fade @ 8 frames = ultra-tight overlaps)  
